27-29 December - Fettuccine Gianna

- 1   lb cooked fettuccine 
- 1/2 stick butter 
- 1   cup heavy cream
- 1/3 cup grated cheese
- 1   egg, beaten
-     salt, pepper and garlic powder to taste
-     parsley (enough to add obvious color)
-     extra grated cheese for topping

Melt butter in a stainless steel pan or skillet. Toss fettuccine to coat with melted butter. To this add the heavy cream ,grated cheese, egg, salt, pepper, and garlic powder, and parsley. Serve with grated cheese immediately. 